      "title": "Escaper bypass leads to XSS in html/template",
      "descriptions": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "value": "If a trusted template author were to write a \u003cscript\u003e tag containing an empty 'type' attribute or a 'type' attribute with an ASCII whitespace, the execution of the template would incorrectly escape any data passed into the \u003cscript\u003e block."
        }
      ],
      "affected": [
